if you've been feeling alone as a creator, joining & participating in a DAO might give you the sense of belonging & contributing to something greater than yourself that you've been looking for

you don't have to do it alone anymore

DAOs are such a paradigm shift in internet culture

we've all been building our own digital brands across social media. and we've been doing it *alone* for so long.

but contributing to a DAO completely shifts your focus & intent from "me" to "we"

one of the most important traits for a community manager to have is emotional intelligence

responding to community emotion can either build trust or destroy it

learn to make people feel heard, understood, and supported through good & bad times
